rpc.design
Class Unit

java.lang.Object
  rpc.design.Unit

public class Unit
extends java.lang.Object

The unit class consists of a pair of treatment and outcome paths with a common base item. A unit corresponds to a potential dependency in the causal model.

Method Detail

reverse

public Unit reverse()
Construct a new unit by reversing the treatment and outcome paths and standardizing the result. Will return null if the standardized reverse does not exist. If the unit consists of null components, then there is no reverse.

Returns:
a new Unit: outcome -> treatment.
